claim.claim-text:
1. A multi-loop voltage controlled oscillator, comprising:
at least a first two cross-over frequency filters operative to provide the low frequency components of a control signal to a voltage controlled oscillator;
at least another two cross-over frequency filters operative to strip off the high frequency components of the control signal;
a pair of integrators operative to provide the phase characteristics of the control signal in response to the high frequency components of the control signal; and
a phase oscillator operative to phase modulate the output of the voltage controlled oscillator in response to the integrated phase characteristics of the control voltage.
